@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS for easy layout and responsiveness -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin: 50px 0;
        }

        .feature-box {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .feature-box h3 {
                color: #007bff;
            }

            .feature-box p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1>Welcome to the Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS)</h1>
        <p>Your go-to platform for submitting and managing your claims as an Independent Contractor.</p>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Claim")" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Start Claim Submission</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Section -->
    <div class="container feature-section">
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Submit Claim</h3>
            <p>Effortlessly submit your monthly claims with a few clicks.</p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Claim")" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Submit Now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Track Claim Status</h3>
            <p>Track the progress of your claims in real-time.</p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("ClaimResult", "Claim")" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Track Status</a>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>View Claims</h3>
            <p>Review your submitted claims and their statuses.</p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Claim")" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Claims</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <div class="text-center">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Contract Monthly Claim System</p>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Privacy", "Home")">Privacy Policy</a>
    </div>

   
</body>
</html>
Explanation of Index.cshtml:
Hero Section: A large, welcoming section that includes a title, a short description, and a call-to-action (CTA) button that directs users to the claim submission page.
Feature Section: A section with cards that showcase the main features of the website (submit claim, track claim status, view claims). These cards use Bootstrap's grid system for layout and responsiveness.
Footer Section: A simple footer with the copyright notice and a link to the Privacy page.
